#Hitchhiker’s Guide to Securing Cisco
Adapted From From the Book CCENT by Todd Lammle
#Don’t Panic!
All of which that is below can be automatically done by using Autosecure. However, these are here to provide a reference in case such a reference is needed. (For example, when autosecure can’t be used because it would disable a critical service, such as HTTP) Although, autosecure does more.

Make sure you look up interface names using “show ip int brief”! Some commands are interface specific! 
